(But you don't need to spend that much effort to find him.)

868
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:41,800
(I was heartbroken)

869
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:43,480
(when he first left us.)

870
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:46,190
(But I gradually got over him)

871
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,360
(because of you guys.)

872
00:37:49,150 --> 00:37:50,920
(The explosion that happened when I was six)

873
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,320
(impacted my family deeply.)

874
00:37:53,710 --> 00:37:55,010
(But I was also able to encounter you guys)

875
00:37:55,010 --> 00:37:56,320
(because of that.)

876
00:37:57,070 --> 00:37:58,440
(You guys are my friends.)

877
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:00,400
(You guys are a part of my family too.)

878
00:38:10,630 --> 00:38:11,800
Huang Yingzi.

879
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:15,510
Are you trying to take a bite?

880
00:38:16,590 --> 00:38:17,670
Bad girl.

881
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:20,190
Dad will come home in a second.

882
00:38:20,630 --> 00:38:21,480
You're not allowed to take a bite.

883
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:23,400
Got it.

884
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:28,880
Little cake,

885
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:30,760
I'll eat you later.

886
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:31,550
Mr. Huang,

887
00:38:31,550 --> 00:38:34,320
I can have instant noodles at home alone.

888
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:36,480
Your parents instructed me

889
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,400
to bring you to my house for meals

890
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,920
when they weren't around.

891
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:42,360
One, two, three, four, five.

892
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,280
If we include my parents,

893
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:45,630
there are seven people.

894
00:38:45,630 --> 00:38:48,440
How can we divide the cake evenly?

895
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,480
I attend dance lessons.

896
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:51,760
My dance instructor doesn't want me to take too much sweet food.

897
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:53,030
I can choose not to have it.

898
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:55,320
Yifei,

899
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:57,670
we only have cake once per year.

900
00:38:57,960 --> 00:39:01,280
You'll have to wait for one year if you don't have it now.

901
00:39:01,550 --> 00:39:02,960
There are 12 months in a year.

902
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:05,150
Now, there are five of us.

903
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:07,400
If we do some division,

904
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:11,000
that means we can have cake in less than three months.

905
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,320
What does division mean?

906
00:39:13,670 --> 00:39:15,150
Forget about the calculation.

907
00:39:15,150 --> 00:39:16,400
I have an idea.

908
00:39:16,710 --> 00:39:18,280
We just need to divide it into eight slices.

909
00:39:18,280 --> 00:39:20,710
And I'll have one extra slice.

910
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,190
No.

911
00:39:22,190 --> 00:39:23,800
Today's my birthday.

912
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:25,880
I should have the extra slice.

913
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:28,960
Yingzi,

914
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:31,710
your mother prepared so many delicious dishes today.

915
00:39:31,710 --> 00:39:34,480
You won't get to eat too much cake anyway.

916
00:39:34,480 --> 00:39:35,800
Why don't 't we

917
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:37,760
split it into eight slices

918
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:40,550
and keep one slice for you as breakfast for tomorrow?

919
00:39:40,550 --> 00:39:41,280
That's great.

920
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:44,110
This way, I can still celebrate my birthday tomorrow.

921
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:46,710
Mr. Huang, this is unnecessary.

922
00:39:46,710 --> 00:39:48,400
Our house is lively today.

923
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:50,150
A little girl is celebrating her birthday.

924
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,230
There are quite a lot of kids

925
00:39:51,230 --> 00:39:52,760
at our house today.

926
00:39:55,670 --> 00:39:56,590
Here, come in.

927
00:39:57,190 --> 00:39:59,190
Dad, what took you so long?

928
00:39:59,190 --> 00:40:00,550
I'm starving.

929
00:40:01,550 --> 00:40:02,440
Yingzi,

930
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:04,070
I brought you a new friend.

931
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:05,280
His name is Jiang Yi.

932
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:06,800
Hello.

933
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,030
My name is Huang Yingzi.

934
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:14,150
Who is this?

935
00:40:15,190 --> 00:40:16,920
He's the son of our new neighbor.

936
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:18,110
His parents went on a sudden business trip.

937
00:40:18,110 --> 00:40:19,230
I brought him back to have a meal with us.

938
00:40:19,510 --> 00:40:20,150
Sure.

939
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:20,880
Welcome.

940
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:22,800
Come on, time to eat .

941
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:23,840
Time to have dinner,

942
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:24,630
kids.

943
00:40:24,630 --> 00:40:25,550
That's right.

944
00:40:26,110 --> 00:40:26,550
Time to have dinner.

945
00:40:26,550 --> 00:40:27,590
Be careful.

946
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:29,190
I've waited for so long.

947
00:40:29,190 --> 00:40:30,320
Yingzi.

948
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,440
You're the birthday girl.

949
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:34,230
Introduce Jiang Yi to them.

950
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:36,030
My name is Huang Yingzi.

951
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,230
I' m from Class 2.

952
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,710
He doesn't respond

953
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:42,480
when I speak to him.

954
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,070
Dad,

955
00:40:43,070 --> 00:40:45,070
don't tell me he's deaf?

956
00:40:45,070 --> 00:40:46,550
I'm not deaf.

957
00:40:46,550 --> 00:40:47,630
Why didn't you respond to me

958
00:40:47,630 --> 00:40:49,190
when I was speaking to you?

959
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,110
Alright now.

960
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:52,280
Let's all

961
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:54,360
introduce ourselves.

962
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:57,510
Jiang Yi was transferred to your kindergarten not long ago.

963
00:40:57,510 --> 00:40:59,960
You guys will be classmates soon.

964
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:01,070
My name is Fang Mingyu.

965
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:02,280
I'm from Class 2.

966
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,480
I'm from Class 3.

967
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,840
My name is Zhuang Yuan.

968
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,070
I 'm in the same class as Zhuang Yuan.

969
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:07,150
My name is Lan Yifei.

970
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,360
My name is Guan Chao.

971
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:09,550
Jiang Yi,

972
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:11,320
which class were you assigned to?

973
00:41:11,670 --> 00:41:12,440
Class 2.

974
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,000
Great.

975
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,320
He's in the same class as us.

976
00:41:14,760 --> 00:41:16,280
He's a strange guy.

977
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:17,440
There's nothing great about it.

978
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:21,880
Come.

979
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,110
Let's have dinner.

980
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:30,550
Initially, I was supposed to have one extra slice of cake

981
00:41:30,550 --> 00:41:32,320
for breakfast tomorrow.

982
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:34,230
But now, it's gone.

983
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:35,280
Huang Yingzi,

984
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:37,070
how could you say that?

985
00:41:37,070 --> 00:41:38,630
If so, Jiang Yi won' t share his cake with you

986
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:40,400
