987
00:41:41,400 --> 00:41:43,190
Now, there are six of us.

988
00:41:43,190 --> 00:41:45,920
We can have one more cake per year now.

989
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:46,710
Yeah.

990
00:41:46,710 --> 00:41:47,710
That's right.

991
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:49,760
Fine.

992
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:51,760
Although you were a little rude just now,

993
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:53,760
I've forgiven you.

994
00:41:53,760 --> 00:41:55,230
Let's be good friends.

995
00:41:55,630 --> 00:41:57,150
Do you truly wish to be friends with me?

996
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:59,320
Or do you just want to have extra cake?

997
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:01,630
My goodness.

998
00:42:02,510 --> 00:42:03,360
Alright.

999
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:04,760
Let's sing the birthday song

1000
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:08,150
for Yingzi.

1001
00:42:08,150 --> 00:42:09,190
Okay.

1002
00:42:09,190 --> 00:42:11,190
Here we go. One, two, three.

1003
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:29,550
Happy birthday to you

1004
00:42:29,550 --> 00:42:30,150
Blow the candles.

1005
00:42:30,150 --> 00:42:31,000
Nice!

1006
00:42:35,280 --> 00:42:36,000
What happened?

1007
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:38,840
Don't be scared.

1008
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:40,230
Kids, don't be scared.

1009
00:42:40,230 --> 00:42:41,400
Everything's fine.

1010
00:42:44,670 --> 00:42:45,590
Is this Huang?

1011
00:42:45,590 --> 00:42:46,510
Yes, it is me.

1012
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:47,800
Something happened at the factory.

1013
00:42:47,800 --> 00:42:48,480
You guys should come here immediately.

1014
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:49,670
Alright.

1015
00:42:49,670 --> 00:42:50,510
I'll be there right away.

1016
00:42:50,920 --> 00:42:51,800
What happened?

1017
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:52,400
Something happened at the factory.

1018
00:42:52,400 --> 00:42:53,480
They told us to head there now.

1019
00:42:53,480 --> 00:42:54,150
Us?

1020
00:42:54,550 --> 00:42:55,760
What about the kids?
